title: Evergreen Terrace Discography
description:
Evergreen Terrace is a 5 piece melodic metalcore/hardcore band out of Jacksonville, Florida. Some of the current and ex-members of Evergreen Terrace spend some of their time playing in the straight edge band Casey Jones. The band is named after the street where The Simpsons claim residence.

Members:
Andrew Carey - Vocals
Craig Chaney - Guitar, Backing Vocals
Josh James - Guitar
Jason Southwell - Bass
Kyle Mims - Drums
